StartPage_WhyRoboForm_Question1_Text.message:
RoboForm works on %1, not just %2. And it works on %3, including iOS and Android.

%4 Just one click on a RoboForm Login will take you to the website sign-in page, fill your credentials, and hit the submit button on any device. Plus, manage your passwords from our %5 browser extension and web editor.

Additional features your browser doesn't have: secure sharing of passwords, emergency access for a trusted contact, and save and AutoFill any online form. Finally, we offer chat, phone, and 24/7 email support.

StartPage_WhyRoboForm_Question1_Text_3.message: One click is better than five.

StartPage_WhyRoboForm_Question2_Text.message:
Absolutely. %1 Your passwords are encrypted with your own secret key—the RoboForm Master Password which you create. We use AES256 bit encryption with PBKDF2 SHA256.
